Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}距今100年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出現了人類的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們與人類之間存在著壓倒性的力量差距
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類差點陷入滅絕的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}存活下來的人類們建造了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}瑪利亞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}席納之牆 三面城牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從此實現了100年的和平生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在受到巨人襲擊的托洛斯特區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士兵們之所以會受害如此嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也是因為精銳的調查軍團不在的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們在那天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才剛出去牆外調查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是調查軍團的主力部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文團長 請你們把巨人全都殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快看是里維士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他可是一個人的戰力就抵得過一個旅團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}呿 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家充滿羨慕的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果知道了你這有潔癖的個性 一定會幻滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個外面...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就有著巨人們...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次能遇到怎樣的巨人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果奇行種出來的話就太棒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果是奇行種的話這裡就有一隻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}牆外調查以及為了放置補給物資而設置據點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被託付這個任務的調查軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是人類智慧的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為某些才能智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才使得生存率大幅提昇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即使如此每次派兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是會造成超過三成以上的人員損失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而人類跟巨人之間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}依然存在著「實力」的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我看著...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然現在你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想要消滅人類...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過到最後存活下來的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}依然還是人類...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們這些傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一定會...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被里維士官長...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}右側一個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}左側兩個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}增援已經陸續聚集了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}佩托拉 妳去救出底下的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剩下的人全部去支援右翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我去解決左側的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不會讓你太痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次換我這了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對吧 不痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}每個都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我擺出一臉有趣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我乖一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不然我就沒辦法將你的肉...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}整齊地割下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}髒死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}血...止不住...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官..長...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對人類是否有所貢獻了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是我會就這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼都沒貢獻地...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}死去呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你已經表現的非常好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從今以後也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你所留下來的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將會賦予我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我跟你約定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我一定 會將巨人消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這傢伙 他有聽到最後嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他一定聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他看起來很安詳地睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}撤退?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都還沒有推進到極限呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道要我的部下白白地犧牲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人一起以城鎮為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就跟五年前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}城鎮似乎發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}城牆可能又被破壞了也說不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...不應該是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們跟五年前不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}拚命地訓練了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}拚命地思考著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了戰勝他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了不被他們吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好熱...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好熱...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}救救我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}救...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼會這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼我們還是被剝奪了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}生命也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}夢想也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我怎麼可以就這樣放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要殺光他們...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一隻不留地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}用我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這雙手...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要殺光他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從這世上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一隻不留地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我還要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我還要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我還要殺更多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想殺更多...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}更多...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}殺掉你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 身體還能動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}意識還清楚嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把你知道的事情全部說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們一定可以了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他說要「殺你們」...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊 的確是聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙打算要把我們都吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家在說什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個劍是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是指向我們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那不是用來打倒巨人的武器嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼要用那種眼神看我?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是... 怎樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}訓練兵帶好自己的裝備待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}後來好不容易才拿到瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從托洛斯特逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好幾次志願想替大家進行補給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們好不容易才拿到瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那...那麼現在不在這裡的人全部都....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}連那個米卡莎也是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不 我想米卡莎是跟約翰他們一起過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道米卡莎受傷了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們被下了保密命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}保密命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那是什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反正那原本就是瞞不住的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很快的 全人類都會知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果到時候... 還有人類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人本身會以肉體來做為防護壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這點技術科也考慮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但我們依然不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}畢竟這裡是人類與巨人的最前線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.64,Default,*,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一分一秒都不能鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}任務方面沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是 我倒比較擔心負責前線的同伴們的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剛剛的傳令兵也是一臉蒼白的往本部移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是我們只要專心按照當初訓練的 來迎戰就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我聽說五年前和漢尼斯隊長一起逃出來的那三個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如今都成了訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們也在最前線...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不好意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不該說太多的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}每個人都有自己一套存活的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一個擁有高超的戰鬥技術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一個具有強韌的精神力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而另一個則有著聰明的頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們一定還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}葉卡訓練兵!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以及旁邊的阿卡曼和亞魯雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剛才你們所做的 是背叛人類的行為!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們將以你們的性命來審問你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果敢再說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}或是想要逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我將會立刻朝你發射榴彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒有打算手下留情!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就直接問了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的真實身分到底是什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是人類嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是巨人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是什麼問題...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是什麼眼神?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}彷彿在看著怪物似地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道是要我說「我是」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不懂你問這個的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還想裝傻嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有本事你再試一次看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會把你一瞬間轟成渣!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓你沒時間露出真面目!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真面目?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很多人都看到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你從巨人體內出現的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們人類竟然讓你這種來路不明的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}入侵到羅塞之牆裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算你們是國王授予的訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在出現風險的早期就應該加以排除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我這麼做並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說不定當初破壞瑪利亞之牆的那個盔甲巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在還會出現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}目前是我們人類存亡的危機關頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們不能為了你們再分散兵力和時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我將會毫不猶豫地對你發射榴彈砲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}的確 他們的態度很明顯是在反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且看來是得不到什麼有用的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說的對 這只是在浪費兵力和時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在簡單多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要在他化為人類的這段期間內殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的特長是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把肉削下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果有必要我隨時可以露一手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}倘若有人想體驗一下我的特長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那就請他先站上前來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}隊長 那位米卡莎．阿卡曼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}原本跟著我們這些精銳負責後衛的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她的表現足以抵過一百名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果失去她對人類來說會是一大損失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 米卡莎 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎 妳怎麼會和人類對抗呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這狹小的牆壁中 我們到底能夠往哪裡逃啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不管要我對付誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我都會阻止艾連被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}除此之外都不解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們要溝通!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家都還不清楚狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以才會陷入恐慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道只有我認為自己不是巨人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒有到目前為止的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}身體完全無力站不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要是亂開口又可能會沒命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會被人類殺掉?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種荒唐的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且到底是怎樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我從巨人的體內跑出來?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底是怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道那不是夢嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這沒衣服覆蓋的部分可是有長著手的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這不就跟巨人一樣了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼我會...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我再問一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的真實身分到底是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之 我絕對不能回答錯誤...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不然會死的可不只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我從以前就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟你們一樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是人類!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那可就別怪我了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是不得已的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為誰都無法證明...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}自己是不是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}往上面跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別這樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就給你看看我一直把它當作是秘密的地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這把鑰匙你要寸不離身地隨時帶著它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且你每次看到這把鑰匙就要想到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你必須去地下室這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為打針的關係 你會產生記憶障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以現在說明也沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:21:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽好 奪回瑪利亞之牆之後你一定要去地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這股力量到時候會派上用場的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想他們的記憶會教你如何去使用它的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你總有一天到了地下室就會了解到真相的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然那是條艱苛的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但你絕對要到那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果你想拯救大家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就一定要掌控住這股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}幹掉了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連並不是人類的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然阿爾敏挺身辯解
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.07,0:24:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是被恐懼所囚禁而放棄思考的駐紮軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}下達了將艾連處刑的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
